{"tid":352604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓揚言認真研究以導彈襲關島","createTime":"2017-08-09T01:37:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T04:22:15.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49d4a73f1a4ffd06c5d4985be465c16d656b4861","tid":352604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170809/s00005/ab88bf9f0b424deae1e5397928e8aa63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170809%2Fs00005%2Fab88bf9f0b424deae1e5397928e8aa63.jpg&h=734f7052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普指朝鮮極具威脅，已超出一般正常國家，又警告朝鮮若繼續威脅美國，將會以世界從沒見過的怒火及武力打擊朝鮮。相隔數小時後，朝鮮軍方稱正研究瞄準關島周圍發射中程導彈。<br />\n<br />\n朝鮮軍方發聲明，指正研究動用「火星-12」中長程導彈發動攻擊，以壓制關島一帶主要軍事基地，並向美國發出作戰警告。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又指，朝鮮軍方已充分研究並擬定作戰方案，即將向最高司令部報告，又表示只要朝鮮最高領導人金正恩一下決定，軍方將隨時執行作戰方案。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》引述美國官員透露國防情報局的分析，指朝鮮已成功製造可由彈道導彈，包括洲際導彈搭載的小型化核彈頭，對美國及鄰國構成威脅。五角大樓未有回應，但指有兩名美方官員和美國有線電視新聞網確認了該份報告。"},{"pid":"f646f6ee474a2f584f2e31ad4f345ebd9f0e482e","tid":352604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:37:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170809/s00005/1502237245553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170809%2Fs00005%2F1502237245553&d=uv%2Fnv99QntN2KdwFnr6w1F0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ce0f6e90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170809%2Fs00005%2F1502237245553&h=79bad29b\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170809/s00005/1502237245553</a>"},{"pid":"364a87641f1f441984413dc49fec6927c2be84c4","tid":352604,"uid":83906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:38:19.000Z","msg":"我唔明點解個個都咁鐘情口交"},{"pid":"fd28653f4a2585d6bf4c14af89e2757f41ca2038","tid":352604,"uid":50740,"like":0